# Gumbel

> Gumbel distribution.

<section class="usage">

## Usage

```javascript
var gumbel = require( '@stdlib/math/base/dists/gumbel' );
```

#### gumbel

Gumbel distribution.

```javascript
var dist = gumbel;
// returns {...}
```
